AI is an application to mimic person to do a specific thing

AI application learns information from available training data before return result from input

AI can run on many devices eg: web browser, smart phone application, on a Robot, on a car... etc

examples:

- ChatGPT https://openai.com/index/chatgpt/

- Github Copilot

The chapters marked with numbering eg: 2.1, 2.2... is mandatory chappters to learn and build up
